# SocifyMedia — Netlify redirect rules
# Docs: https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/

# --- Force apex domain (non-www) ---
# Tell Netlify the canonical host is socifymedia.in.
# (Also set this in: Netlify dashboard → Domain management → Primary domain.)
https://www.socifymedia.in/*   https://socifymedia.in/:splat   301!

# --- URL normalisation: legacy old patterns → current canonical ---
# Just in case a different slug ever existed historically, alias variants:
/digital-marketing-chandigarh         /digital-marketing-services-chandigarh/   301!
/digital-marketing-agency-chandigarh  /digital-marketing-services-chandigarh/   301!
/digital-marketing-gurgaon            /digital-marketing-agency-gurugram/       301!
/digital-marketing-agency-gurgaon     /digital-marketing-agency-gurugram/       301!
/digital-marketing-bengaluru          /digital-marketing-agency-bangalore/      301!
/digital-marketing-agency-bengaluru   /digital-marketing-agency-bangalore/      301!

# --- 404 fallback (must be the LAST rule) ---
/*   /404.html   404
